DESCRIPTION:Fall back into what you love or discover something new at the J’s fall classes and programs for children and adults of all ages! \nAquatics | Art | Culinary Arts | Dance | Fitness | Gymnastics | Jewish Learning | Specialty Classes | Sports & Rec | Teens | Tennis | Theatre  \nMember Registration Opens | July 13 at 9:00 AM    \nPublic Registration Opens | July 16 at 9:00 AM     \nFirst Week of Classes | August 23-28   \nLast Week of Classes | December 14-18 
