SUMMARY:Summer Film: Hill “Halfon” Doesn’t Answer
DESCRIPTION:Hill “Halfon” Doesn’t Answer Directed by Asi Dayan (1976)  \nComedy | 92 Minutes | Hebrew with English subtitles \nJoin us for the celebration of the 50th anniversary of the legendary film which became the greatest cult film in the history of Israeli cinema. In this satirical cult-classic\, a reserve unit in the Israel-controlled Sinai is less than five miles from the Egyptian front lines. However\, the Israelis are hardly concerned with the Egyptians\, as half of the Reserve-niks are just happy to get away from their homes and essentially go camping in uniform\, while the other half goes crazy in hilarious fashion.
URL:https://www.erjcchouston.org/event/summer-film-hill-halfon-doesnt-answer/
LOCATION:Kaplan Theatre @ the J\, 5601 S. Braeswood\, Houston\, TX\, 77096
CATEGORIES:Arts & Culture
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://www.erjcchouston.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/Calendar-Event-Banners-for-Website-31.png
ORGANIZER;CN="Guy Cohen":MAILTO:gcohen@erjcchouston.org
GEO:29.6738082;-95.4839865
