SUMMARY:Open Gym & Tot Shabbat
DESCRIPTION:For kids ages 0-5 and their families \nCelebrate Shabbat with your friends and family with open gym in the gymnastics center followed by musical services. \nOpen gym will begin at 10:00 AM in the gymnastics center\, followed by music and services at 11:00 AM in the atrium of the Samuels Family Community Pavilion. \nRSVPs are required and spaces are limited. \n 
URL:https://www.erjcchouston.org/event/open-gym-tot-shabbat-6/
