SUMMARY:Yoga Deconstructed
DESCRIPTION:Explore the fundamentals of yoga through a detailed breakdown of common poses and alignment principles. Learn techniques to support joint safety\, improve body awareness and enhance your practice with greater confidence and skill. Whether you’re new to yoga or looking to refine your practice\, this workshop offers valuable insights for all levels. \nRegistration link coming soon.
URL:https://www.erjcchouston.org/event/yoga-deconstructed/
LOCATION:Evelyn Rubenstein JCC\, 5601 S. Braeswood\, Houston\, TX\, 77096\, United States
CATEGORIES:Health & Wellness
