SUMMARY:Sweathearts: A Fitness Class Date Night\, Tu B'Av Edition
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate the holiday of love with a workout designed for two! Join Meryl and Adam for a fun-filled evening of partner exercises\, team challenges\, laughs and plenty of movement. No fitness experience required—just bring your sweetheart\, best friend or favorite workout partner and get ready to sweat\, connect and have a great time together!
URL:https://www.erjcchouston.org/event/sweathearts-a-fitness-class-date-night-tu-bav-edition/
